    "## Part 2: Agent Service — MVP Summit Concierge\n",
    "\n",
    "The agent uses **MCPTool** to connect to the knowledge base. Each query triggers:\n",
    "1. Query planning & decomposition\n",
    "2. Multi-source retrieval (sessions + campus guide)\n",
    "3. Semantic reranking\n",
    "4. Answer synthesis with citations"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 4,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "✓ Agent helper function ready\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "def ask_agent(agent_name: str, question: str) -> str:\n",
    "    \"\"\"Send a question to a Foundry Agent Service agent and return the response.\"\"\"\n",
    "    # Create conversation\n",
    "    conversation = openai_client.conversations.create()\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # Send query\n",
    "    response = openai_client.responses.create(\n",
    "        conversation=conversation.id,\n",
    "        input=question,\n",
    "        extra_body={\"agent_reference\": {\"name\": agent_name, \"type\": \"agent_reference\"}},\n",
    "    )\n",
    "    return response.output_text\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"✓ Agent helper function ready\")"
   ]
  },
